2026-02-13 17:03:26.025 -05:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (1ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT `c`.`Id`, `c`.`active_mobile_session`, `c`.`blocked`, `c`.`bot_id`, `c`.`bot_response`, `c`.`closed_at`, `c`.`created_at`, `c`.`expires_at`, `c`.`is_with_ai`, `c`.`last_active_at`, `c`.`last_message`, `c`.`mobile_device_type`, `c`.`mobile_joined_at`, `c`.`public_user_id`, `c`.`status`, `c`.`Title`, `c`.`updated_at`, `c`.`user_id`, `c`.`user_message`, `b`.`id`, `b`.`ai_model_config_id`, `b`.`api_key`, `b`.`bot_template_id`, `b`.`created_at`, `b`.`description`, `b`.`ia_provider_id`, `b`.`is_active`, `b`.`is_deleted`, `b`.`is_ready`, `b`.`name`, `b`.`style_id`, `b`.`updated_at`, `b`.`user_id`, `t0`.`RawContent`, `t0`.`Timestamp`, `t0`.`Type`, `t0`.`c`
FROM `Conversations` AS `c`
INNER JOIN `Bots` AS `b` ON `c`.`bot_id` = `b`.`id`
LEFT JOIN LATERAL (
    SELECT `t`.`RawContent`, `t`.`Timestamp`, `t`.`Type`, 1 AS `c`
    FROM (
        SELECT `m`.`message_text` AS `RawContent`, `m`.`created_at` AS `Timestamp`, 'text' AS `Type`
        FROM `Messages` AS `m`
        WHERE `m`.`conversation_id` = `c`.`Id`
        UNION ALL
        SELECT `c0`.`file_name` AS `RawContent`, `c0`.`uploaded_at` AS `Timestamp`, CASE
            WHEN `c0`.`file_type` LIKE 'image%' THEN 'image'
            ELSE 'file'
        END AS `Type`
        FROM `chat_uploaded_files` AS `c0`
        WHERE `c0`.`conversation_id` = `c`.`Id`
    ) AS `t`
    ORDER BY `t`.`Timestamp` DESC

SELECT `c`.`Id`, `c`.`active_mobile_session`, `c`.`blocked`, `c`.`bot_id`, `c`.`bot_response`, `c`.`closed_at`, `c`.`created_at`, `c`.`expires_at`, `c`.`is_with_ai`, `c`.`last_active_at`, `c`.`last_message`, `c`.`mobile_device_type`, `c`.`mobile_joined_at`, `c`.`public_user_id`, `c`.`status`, `c`.`Title`, `c`.`updated_at`, `c`.`user_id`, `c`.`user_message`, `b`.`id`, `b`.`ai_model_config_id`, `b`.`api_key`, `b`.`bot_template_id`, `b`.`created_at`, `b`.`description`, `b`.`ia_provider_id`, `b`.`is_active`, `b`.`is_deleted`, `b`.`is_ready`, `b`.`name`, `b`.`style_id`, `b`.`updated_at`, `b`.`user_id`, `t0`.`RawContent`, `t0`.`Timestamp`, `t0`.`Type`, `t0`.`c`
FROM `Conversations` AS `c`
INNER JOIN `Bots` AS `b` ON `c`.`bot_id` = `b`.`id`
LEFT JOIN LATERAL (
    SELECT `t`.`RawContent`, `t`.`Timestamp`, `t`.`Type`, 1 AS `c`
    FROM (
        SELECT `m`.`message_text` AS `RawContent`, `m`.`created_at` AS `Timestamp`, 'text' AS `Type`
        FROM `Messages` AS `m`
        WHERE `m`.`conversation_id` = `c`.`Id`
        UNION ALL
        SELECT `c0`.`file_name` AS `RawContent`, `c0`.`uploaded_at` AS `Timestamp`, CASE
            WHEN `c0`.`file_type` LIKE 'image%' THEN 'image'
            ELSE 'file'
        END AS `Type`
        FROM `chat_uploaded_files` AS `c0`
        WHERE `c0`.`conversation_id` = `c`.`Id`
    ) AS `t`
    ORDER BY `t`.`Timestamp` DESC
    LIMIT 1
) AS `t0` ON TRUE

INNER JOIN `Bots` AS `b` ON `c`.`bot_id` = `b`.`id`
LEFT JOIN LATERAL (
    SELECT `t`.`RawContent`, `t`.`Timestamp`, `t`.`Type`, 1 AS `c`
    FROM (
        SELECT `m`.`message_text` AS `RawContent`, `m`.`created_at` AS `Timestamp`, 'text' AS `Type`
        FROM `Messages` AS `m`
        WHERE `m`.`conversation_id` = `c`.`Id`
        UNION ALL
        SELECT `c0`.`file_name` AS `RawContent`, `c0`.`uploaded_at` AS `Timestamp`, CASE
            WHEN `c0`.`file_type` LIKE 'image%' THEN 'image'
            ELSE 'file'
        END AS `Type`
        FROM `chat_uploaded_files` AS `c0`
        WHERE `c0`.`conversation_id` = `c`.`Id`
    ) AS `t`
    ORDER BY `t`.`Timestamp` DESC
    LIMIT 1
) AS `t0` ON TRUE

SELECT `c`.`Id`, `c`.`active_mobile_session`, `c`.`blocked`, `c`.`bot_id`, `c`.`bot_response`, `c`.`closed_at`, `c`.`created_at`, `c`.`expires_at`, `c`.`is_with_ai`, `c`.`last_active_at`, `c`.`last_message`, `c`.`mobile_device_type`, `c`.`mobile_joined_at`, `c`.`public_user_id`, `c`.`status`, `c`.`Title`, `c`.`updated_at`, `c`.`user_id`, `c`.`user_message`, `b`.`id`, `b`.`ai_model_config_id`, `b`.`api_key`, `b`.`bot_template_id`, `b`.`created_at`, `b`.`description`, `b`.`ia_provider_id`, `b`.`is_active`, `b`.`is_deleted`, `b`.`is_ready`, `b`.`name`, `b`.`style_id`, `b`.`updated_at`, `b`.`user_id`, `t0`.`RawContent`, `t0`.`Timestamp`, `t0`.`Type`, `t0`.`c`
FROM `Conversations` AS `c`
INNER JOIN `Bots` AS `b` ON `c`.`bot_id` = `b`.`id`
LEFT JOIN LATERAL (
    SELECT `t`.`RawContent`, `t`.`Timestamp`, `t`.`Type`, 1 AS `c`
    FROM (
        SELECT `m`.`message_text` AS `RawContent`, `m`.`created_at` AS `Timestamp`, 'text' AS `Type`
        FROM `Messages` AS `m`
        WHERE `m`.`conversation_id` = `c`.`Id`
        UNION ALL
        SELECT `c0`.`file_name` AS `RawContent`, `c0`.`uploaded_at` AS `Timestamp`, CASE
            WHEN `c0`.`file_type` LIKE 'image%' THEN 'image'
            ELSE 'file'
        END AS `Type`
        FROM `chat_uploaded_files` AS `c0`
        WHERE `c0`.`conversation_id` = `c`.`Id`
    ) AS `t`
    ORDER BY `t`.`Timestamp` DESC
    LIMIT 1
) AS `t0` ON TRUE
